2951struct EnumTraits<IPC::MessageName> {
2952 template<typename T>
2953 static std::enable_if_t<sizeof(T) == sizeof(IPC::MessageName) && std::is_unsigned_v<T>, bool> isValidEnum(T messageName)
2954 {
2955 if (messageName > WTF::enumToUnderlyingType(IPC::MessageName::Last))
2956 return false;
2957 return IPC::isValidMessageName(static_cast<IPC::MessageName>(messageName));
2958 }
2959};
